                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6327" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0982</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8452 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">蚂蚁金服上市折戟启示—控制风险，拥抱监管</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Enlightenment of ant financial services listing failure  -- control risks and embrace supervision</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">张鲁秀，史正义，刘德胜，惠朋，韩丹</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">济南大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">蚂蚁金融服务集团</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">金融科技；金融创新；金融风险；政府监管</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Fintech；financial innovation；financial risk；government supervise</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">成立于2014年10月的蚂蚁金融服务集团，依靠阿里的生态圈取得了长足的发展，并于2020年7月申请在港股上市。而2020年11月3日，深交所和上交所紧急叫停了蚂蚁集团的上市计划。暂停蚂蚁金服上市引发了业界、学界关于金融科技创新与金融监管的大讨论。本文以蚂蚁金服暂停上市这一事件为主线，对金融科技和蚂蚁金服进行了简要介绍，并从蚂蚁金服准备上市到暂停上市的事件中反思蚂蚁金服自身以及上市后可能蕴含的风险、风险来源，及蚂蚁金服在监管下的应对举措。本案例旨在通过对蚂蚁金服暂停上市事件的介绍，让学生深刻理解其经营模式中蕴含的巨大金融风险，引导学生对未来金融风险监管与金融科技企业发展进行思考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Ant Financial Services Group, founded in October 2014, has made great progress relying on Alibaba&#39;s ecosystem, and applied for listing in Hong Kong stocks in July 2020. However, on November 3, 2020, Shenzhen Stock Exchange and Shanghai Stock Exchange urgently suspended the listing plan of Ant Group. The suspension of Ant Financial Services Group &#39; listing has triggered a great discussion in the industry and academia on financial technology innovation and financial supervision. Taking the suspension of ant financial services as the main line, this paper briefly introduces financial technology and ant financial services, and reflects on ant financial services itself, the possible risks and risk sources after listing, and the response measures of ant financial services under supervision from the event of ant financial services preparing for listing to suspension of listing. This case aims to make students deeply understand the huge financial risks contained in its business model and guide students to think about the future financial risk supervision and the development of financial technology enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《金融风险管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">信用风险；交易结构风险；系统性风险；资产证券化；联合贷款；监管科技；监管沙盒；穿透式监管；科技金融与金融科技；大数据征信</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-06</td>
                            </tr>
